cross multiple services, particularly cartservice, frontend, and shippingservice pods.",\n  "time_series_analysis": {\n    "metric_name": "error_ratio",\n    "pattern": "sudden_spike",\n    "critical_timestamps": ["2025-06-05 18:10:05"],\n    "value_change": "0.0 → 28.48 (frontend), 0.0 → 22.59 (cartservice), 0.0 → 49.56 (shippingservice)"\n  },\n  "contradictions": [\n    {\n      "evidence1": "User requested verification of node memory pressure metrics",\n      "evidence2": "Node-level infrastructure metrics not available in dataset for this time period",\n      "verification_needed": "Cannot verify node memory pressure as requested; only service-level APM metrics are available"\n    }\n  ],\n  "next_verification": {\n    "action": "check_logs",\n    "reason": "High error ratios suggest application-level failures rather than infrastructure memory pressure",\n    "suggested_metrics": ["pod_processes"],\n    "suggested_log_keywords": ["Error", "exception", "timeout", "connection refused"]\n  }\n}\n```'}
